{
  "stem": "1918.4",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But there wasn't a single person that I knew of who was hidden in my town.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And our former customer, a great friend who proclaimed always his friendship and his willingness to help when the-- when the time comes around, when the bell will toll, he was nowhere to be found.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Yes, I have a lot of hard feelings, a lot of bitterness about it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I know-- I certainly don't know of any help for my family.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "None whatsoever.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I understand there were two transports.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I heard the figure of 8,000.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I really don't know, together with the villagers.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But there were two transports, and I don't know if we were in the first or the second.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But we left on May 29, and the reason I know that particularly well, because my birthday is on May 28.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that was the day we were packing for this big unknown journey, and my mother's eyes were filled with such sorrow.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And every time she looked at her birthday baby, instead of birthday cake, I was given something to pile my clothes in to go on what they called-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] what was that again?",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Resettlement, with all its ominous connotations.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we were taken to the railroad station, and together-- the gendarmes were the lackeys, the helping hand for the Nazis.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And surrounded by, at this time, with enough killing power-- bayonets and-- and-- what are they called-- what are they called?",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Rifles?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Rifles, enough to kill 10 times the size of our ghetto.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then-- then we were piled into the cattle cars.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Non-Jews?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were so miserable, I don't remember whether people were going-- I know that once we were in the cattle car, as we rode along into the night, people-- some people went crazy.",
      "word_count": 33
    }
  ],
